title: Fremont single family home now ready for move in!
posting_body: ['Address-40418 Vogel Court Fremont, CA. 94538', 'Rent-$3,100', 'Deposit-$3,200', 'Bedrooms-3', 'Bathrooms-1', 'Square Feet-950', 'This 3 bedroom 1 bathroom Single family home is located right next to Lake Elizabeth in Fremont.', "It's perfect house for commuters.", 'This home comes with a 1 car garage also.', 'The home comes with the following appliances including, Refrigerator, dishwasher, washer/dryer, & oven/stove there for your use.', 'There are 3 spacious bedrooms, t& 1 full bathroom.', "There's hardwood flooring throughout, and a huge back yard.", 'This Home is located next to a ton of things.', 'Driving minutes away from 84 (Dumbarton Bridge), highway 880, highway 680, Lake Elizabeth, Fremont Library, Fremont Hub, Mission San Jose, Ohlone College, Mission Peak, tons of places to eat and much more.', 'Please give me a call to set up a viewing of this beautiful home.', 'Rental Features', '-Family Room', '-Dishwasher', '-Refrigerator', '-Oven/Stove', '-Washer/Dryer', '-Garbage Disposal', '-Laundry Area Inside Garage', '-Fenced backyard area', '-1 car garage', 'Lease Terms-1 Year Lease, NO smoking, NO pets.', 'Qualifications-650+ credit score from anyone 18+ living in the unit, a combined gross household income that triples the rental price, & we check prior rental history.', "Properties can't be rented sight unseen.", "Once you've seen the property and would like to move forward with application process, you'll be able to do so through our website.", '<URL>, click available Homes for rent, click Fremont office, click Fremont, click apply now on Vogel Court.', 'Renters insurance is required.', 'Best Property Management INC', 'Agent-Ryan Alter DRE License # 01769898', '<URL>']
